{
  "keyword": "RMVWSE",
  "description": "Remove Work Station Entry (RMVWSE)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "SBSD",
      "description": "Subsystem description",
      "help": "Subsystem description (SBSD)\n\nSpecifies the name and library of the subsystem description containing the work station job entry that is removed.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Subsystem description\n\nNote: The following IBM-supplied objects are not valid on this parameter:\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": true,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*LIBL",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "SBSD",
          "description": "Subsystem description",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": true,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        }
      ],
      "positional": 1
    },
    {
      "name": "WRKSTN",
      "description": "Work station name",
      "help": "Work station name (WRKSTN)\n\nSpecifies the name of the work station used by the subsystem. The device description name that was specified in the Create Device Desc (Display) (CRTDEVDSP) command associated with the work station is the name used.\n\nDouble-Byte Character Set Considerations: For double-byte character set (DBCS), a work station whose type is 5555 must be specified for either this parameter or the Work station type (WRKSTNTYPE) parameter, but not for both.\n\nNote: Specifying a generic work station name does not result in multiple entries being added, changed, or removed.\n\nA value must be specified on either this parameter or the Work station type (WRKSTNTYP) parameter, but not for both.",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "maxLength": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "WRKSTNTYPE",
      "description": "Work station type",
      "help": "Work station type (WRKSTNTYPE)\n\nSpecifies the type of work station associated with the entry being added, changed, or removed. This entry applies to all work stations of this type that do not have specific entries for an individual work station.\n\nA value must be specified on either this parameter or the Work station name (WRKSTN) parameter, but not for both.",
      "inputType": "dropdown",
